crc-hash provides header-only CRC32 and MD5 hash functions.

Usage:
    find_package(crc-hash CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE crc-hash::crc-hash)

Example:
    #include <crc-hash/crc32.hpp>
    #include <crc-hash/md5.hpp>
    auto c = hash::crc32("hello");
    auto m = hash::md5("hello");
    auto cf = hash::crc32_file("file.bin");
